# Tribal Handicrafts Ecommerce 🪶

A simple ecommerce frontend project showcasing authentic tribal handicrafts, built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript** — no frameworks or backend.

## 🔗 Live Demo
> [Add GitHub Pages link after deployment]

## 🧰 Features
- 🏠 Home page with featured products
- 🛍️ Browse and add items to cart
- 🔐 Login / Sign up (stored in localStorage)
- 👤 Account management (basic mock)
- 🛒 Cart with total calculation
- 🛠️ Admin panel to add products (local-only)
- 📱 Responsive design

